 \"from\": 239, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast logistical and security challenges\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"such an ambitious event\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"130 people\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the spectacular floating parade due to set off along the Seine on Friday night [from 7.30pm South African time], President Emmanuel Macron will hope Lallement's doubts prove ill-founded.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.47616749050588e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_time\", \"score\": 0.9999999884794307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"African time\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_time\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spectacular floating parade\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday night\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"Lallement's doubts\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the beginning, it seemed to be a crazy and not very serious idea,\\\" Macron told foreign reporters at the Elysee palace on Monday.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma