d they have so far foiled two suspected attacks.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"no direct threat\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"two suspected attacks\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to three billion people are expected to tune in for the opening ceremony, in which athletes will sail 5.6km down the Seine against one of the world's most stunning backdrops.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.47616749050588e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Up to three billion people\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most stunning backdrops\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have largely kept their plans for the ceremony under wraps, but Thomas Jolly, artistic director for the event, spoke this week about \\\"a large fresco\\\" celebrating \\\"the relationship Paris and France maintains with the world\\\".\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9817786176374955, \"rank\": 0.017540434526908677, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.46237121271299e-21, \"tex