\": 1523, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether France pulls it off remains to be seen.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9925277201050108, \"rank\": 0.0075137929714961076, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting everyone on board with the idea pitched by Paris 2024 chief Tony Estanguet to Macron in 2019 was a major battle.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.693978380538304e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1704, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2108493213121905e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"a major battle\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea came to Estanguet, a three-time Olympics canoeing champion, after he witnessed the opening ceremony of the 2018 Youth Olympics held in the streets of Buenos Aires in Argentina and attended by more than 200,000 people, his advisers said.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999979942151292, \"rank\": 2.0057863278421676e-06, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}, {\"begin\": 1916, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9997229908474705, \"rank\": 0.0002770645143486244, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-time Olympics\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"champion\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Youth Olympics\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200,000 people\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"his advisers\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet wanted to throw \\\"away the rule book\\\" for Paris 2024, they said.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.693978380538304e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"the rule book\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He tasked Paris 2024 executive director Thierry Reboul, a former Air France advertising chief in charge of the Olympic ceremony, with finding an original idea.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.693978380538304e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5831471859725924e-24, \"text\": \"Thierry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\"}, {\"begin\": 2127, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.727064384137765e-32, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ceremony\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"an original idea\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Inspiration struck in 2019 when Reboul was strolling along the Seine and thought the opening ceremony would take place on the river.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2286, \"end\": 2291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.47616749050588e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Inspiration\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"Reboul\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris mayor Anne Hidalgo told Reuters she was keen from the start.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.46237121271299e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2369, \"end\": 2381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.387365437105404e-18, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But not everyone agreed.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aside from Lallement, police unions were also against the high-risk river ceremony, union officials said.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lallement\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"police unions\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the high-risk river ceremony\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"union officials\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Macron was immediately seduced by the idea, and pushed sceptical police and intelligence officials to make it happen, sources close to the president said.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2108493213121905e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"sceptical police\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligence officials\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"sources\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to know what you think, I want to know how we can do it',\\\" a source close to Macron recalled him saying.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2813, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2108493213121905e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron pledged to give police more headcount to secure the event.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2108493213121905e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"more headcount\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also commissioned a confidential \\\"feasibility report\\\" which in 2021 concluded the Seine ceremony was possible under certain conditions, with fewer spectators and more police.\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.47616749050588e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a confidential \\\"feasibility report\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"certain conditions\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer spectators\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"more police\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The president made the announcement public in late 2021 to ensure there would be no going back, the source close to him said, but has said there are back-up plans if the event can not proceed.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The president\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"the source\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"back-up plans\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many foreign delegations expressed scepticism, and at one point some threatened to cancel their attendance, another French source with knowledge of the matter said.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3397, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6773209996618184, \"rank\": 0.4600263185829735, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many foreign delegations\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"scepticism\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"their attendance\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3425}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They were told no stone would be left unturned,\\\" the source said, adding French authorities decided to be \\\"over zealous\\\" by deploying 45,000 police to secure the event, more than triple what is used for a regular Bastille Day celebration in the entire Paris region.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3521, \"end\": 3527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6773209996618184, \"rank\": 0.4600263185829735, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3700, \"end\": 3705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.46237121271299e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no stone\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"the source\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3507}, {\"ngram\": \"45,000 police\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"a regular Bastille Day celebration\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 36